Willoughby Ave., north side, west from Tompkins Ave., showing at the N.W. corner, the Tompkins Ave. M.E. Church, now a synagogue,
known as the Congregation Ohel Moshe Cheirathhelm.
April 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
